title: 10 Takeaways from Week 9!
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 9!
description:
DJ and Bucky break down the week that was with their top 10 takeaways from week 9, including – Is it time for Lamar to start in Baltimore (:30), if you didn’t know, now you know, the Patriots are one of the most creative offenses in the NFL after a stellar win against the Packers (2:30), New Orleans has all the components to be a Super Bowl team (6:20), Kareem Hunt should be in the MVP convo (9:30), Pittsburgh can win with or without Lev Bell (22:05) and lastly, watch out, the Bears are playoff ready (29:00)!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
